title: 1957 - The Year In Christian Music (Bundle 01)
description:
-----------------------------------------------------------------------
1957 - THE YEAR IN CHRISTIAN MUSIC
-----------------------------------------------------------------------

If we do the math, 1957 was 57 years ago.  Perhaps that older than many of us today.  And although six albums doesn't begin to represent the scope of music being recorded 57 years ago, unfortunately I only have access to these six albums today.  So for the sake of sharing, I've turned them into a 1957 offering.

There are 6 albums being shared today, including...

 * Big John Hall - 1957 - If God Is Dead
 * Chuck Wagon Gang, The - 1957 - Sacred Songs
 * Jack Holcomb - 1957 - I Have A Song
 * Various - 1957 - All-Night Sing 1-4-57
 * Various - 1957 - All-Night Sing 2-1-57
 * Various - 1957 - All-Night Sing 3-1-57

For Him,
TorrentTracts, May 2014
